Host address for api will be set via vite environment variable see : https://vitejs.dev/guide/env-and-mode.html

Note: You must create custom environment variables beginning with VITE_. Environment variables are defined in the root directory of this project in the .env file.

useage: 
    console.log(import.meta.env.VITE_SOME_KEY) // 123

to start the project:
    npm run dev
